			<action-date date="20080303">March 3, 2008</action-date>
			<action-desc><sponsor name-id="S213">Mr. Akaka</sponsor> introduced the
			 following bill; which was read twice and referred to the
			 <committee-name committee-id="SSVA00">Committee on Veterans'
			 Affairs</committee-name></action-desc>
